  "3123980": {
    "name": "SILENT EXPRESS",
    "steam_appid": 3123980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/feb57194c473f318e8f686a12f894e87.avif?t=1763804378\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘客在一座墓地中睁开眼睛。他们被不确定和恐惧所包围。他们的任务是找到并销毁一枚放射性炸弹。这场危险的旅程由火车开始，但这不是一段普通的旅行。每一站都有新的谜团；每节车厢里都潜藏着新的噩梦。他们遇到的列车员和令人毛骨悚然的事件让任务更加复杂。受炸弹影响，火车被带入未知的维度。每一站都隐藏着过去的黑暗秘密和艰难考验。这趟旅程不仅是一个任务；也是一场寻找自我身份的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/47b1c7a8cd204532476eb034dbcede97.poster.avif?t=1763804378\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/47b1c7a8cd204532476eb034dbcede97.webm?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/47b1c7a8cd204532476eb034dbcede97.mp4?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/75cb650a1db35a35e9e37a670ed8f161.avif?t=1763804378\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场独特的列车冒险中，你不仅仅是从一个车厢移动到另一个车厢。有些门会通向不同的世界、互动和支线故事。当你踏入一个看似普通的车厢时，你会突然发现自己身处一个完全不同的地方，并与其他玩家分享这一经历。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/bbf5924e7fad0718a0ed5cbb9e0067b8.poster.avif?t=1763804378\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/bbf5924e7fad0718a0ed5cbb9e0067b8.webm?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/bbf5924e7fad0718a0ed5cbb9e0067b8.mp4?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/c5ba696325119bd4ad5acd0cf974bc5d.avif?t=1763804378\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >车站为旅程增添了额外的兴奋感。每个车站都是通向黑暗秘密的门户，这些门后隐藏着随机的生物。这些生物守护着车站深处的隐藏危机。玩家必须发现有用的物品，并找到拆除炸弹所需的工具包。时间至关重要；任务必须在列车出发前完成。在这场与时间的赛跑中，找到炸弹并生存下去！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/3d84b5b5d3589386e861461ce5770c50.poster.avif?t=1763804378\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/3d84b5b5d3589386e861461ce5770c50.webm?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123980/extras/3d84b5b5d3589386e861461ce5770c50.mp4?t=1763804378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
